This is the Debian packaged version of the Perl module Net::FTPServer.
The upstream authors are:
	Richard Jones (rich@annexia.org),
	Rob Brown (bbb@cpan.org),
	Keith Turner (keitht at silvaco.com),
	Azazel (azazel at azazel.net),
and many others.

Chip Salzenberg <chip@debian.org> created this Debian package using
original Net::FTPServer sources, as found on the Comprehensive Perl
Archive Network (CPAN) <URL:http://cpan.org/>.  The Debian Perl
packaging tool "dh-make-perl" was of great help.

libnet-ftpserver-perl is released under the GNU General Public
License.  On a Debian GNU/Linux systems, the complete text of this
license may be found in the file /usr/share/common-licenses/GPL.
